# Cafeteria-Ordering-System
A functional ordering system which allows users to create their order/make payment/provide feedback while manager can modify menu/register customer/view payment and feedback.

Customer GUI:
1. Customer login page
2. Menu page
3. Profile page
4. Receipt page
5. Cart page
6. Payment page
7. Feedback page

Manager GUI:
1. Manager login page
2. Menu modification page
3. Customer registration page
4. Payment overview page
5. Feedback overview page

Common GUI:
1. Main menu page

Text files:
1. customer info.txt
2. menu.txt
3. receipt.txt
4. feedback.txt

